{"tid":1911181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔reading拎u? 唔好再曲解gPhone意思啦","createTime":"2020-03-05T07:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:18.000Z","uid":203685,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3252c50d7d77f64592b5b1922c49a2d62eb540","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"之前唔小心開左去吹水台 依家開多次<br />\n<br />\n懶嘅直接睇最底紅字<br />\n<br />\n話說幾日前有依個post<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒 : 唔好再去建制Page俾嬲嬲 thx<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人睇完依個post 就叫人唔撚好去東方同cctvb嘅廣告商個到派嬲洗版<br />\n<br />\n但係 事實係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnELojD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnELojD.jpg&h=fcfcfaaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地睇清楚啦 黃之鋒係叫你地唔好去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">建制Page</span></span>俾嬲嬲炸<br />\n<br />\n依家d廣告商嘅page 係唔撚係建制page呀<br />\n<br />\n我出左個post叫人抵制東方廣告商 屌老味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHbFcdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHbFcdv.jpg&h=41d15803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個comment 都有348個正評 想問係咩事<br />\n<br />\n政府黑警民建聯唔怕核突，因為佢地唔駛向人民負責任；廣告商怕核突，因為消費者會令佢地負責任。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">以後見到建制藍絲page 可以學黃之鋒講嘅咁做 但係唔該大家繼續去藍媒嘅廣告商派嬲洗版互like comment</span></span><br />\n<br />\nthx<br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果語氣重左 好對唔住 因為我真係好驚以後都冇人幫手抵制cctvb 同東方嘅廣告商"},{"pid":"3f97a58ebc54fa2842032a1a7e6f9bc000f6ec3a","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"睇完就做野啦<br />\n<br />\n【TVB任務，晒你幾秒】今日洗版精選 - 添寧，透濕能力差 (4 Mar)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910258</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57855736c969fd9266e343c9a312d2fba08262b3","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"推俾更多人知依樣野 唔想再咁多人誤會"},{"pid":"87a294d12f0cbfea2c55f86177fe32cab9454d6a","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"抵制東方link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/boycottoncc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fboycottoncc&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a6ba4cdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/boycottoncc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵制TVB link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaqwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=a801331d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"4ee2ecd7ce6e4ff976d49fdea31684fe4b2ffe0c","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"901690685ad42606c2b02d788135303b40245c21","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"屌 又開左去吹水台"},{"pid":"c9adbda7ef30d606abbed9303b77d6a3c44ddf97","tid":1911181,"uid":101260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"幫手推 之前做過幾次任務 加油"},{"pid":"321dae9d2dcd804de692efbdfa07320b33dcbdd1","tid":1911181,"uid":307315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔join 任務，啲商家係冇原因去撤tvb廣告咖</span><br />\n其實嗰次audi咁快撤tvb廣告係因為大家去左洗版，po佢唔全，連大陸嘅安全測試都可以fail 嘅舊聞。事實上啲商家整FB page 都係想做online marketing 去推自己嗰page 吸客同留客，如果啲客係page 發現間公司嘅仆街舊聞可能就會走，直搞到佢online marketing 做唔成之餘仲少左個客。 audi嗰次嗰反應其實好typical，佢第一時間去del comment 而唔係回應，因為人地賣車要sell 安全同可靠，大家去洗版舊事重提真係會嚇到佢地以為又要處理多次啲醜聞，del 唔哂先宣報撤廣告。同埋買車呢啲嘢唔平，好多人做online research先去買，所以online marketing對佢地真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n第二就係大家亂入個Page 會搞亂佢完本嘅engagement， 因為好多時啲page 會落ads 係同過嗰page 有engagement 嘅人度，結果嗰ad就去左杯佢地嘅手足而唔係target customers. 加上FB 應該係會估嗰page 比較受乜人歡迎而幫佢地啲post show 落乜人嘅feed 到，例如奶粉page 多數target 媽媽，但有班細路同男人就入去，咁FB 就會以為嗰page 其實開始受細路同男人歡迎，show 多啲佢啲post 去細路同男人，打亂佢地啲online marketing <br />\n<br />\n所以，題外話，無論用真ac定假ac都係咁阻住間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算嗰page 嘅engagement高左都冇用，因為佢地唔係林鄭，唔可以咁唔要面"},{"pid":"f7f54b2473044e2783c855e2ed59f1720457548c","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"57855736c969fd9266e343c9a312d2fba08262b3","tid":1911181,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"推俾更多人知依樣野 唔想再咁多人誤會"}}